wayback (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Stable release 1.0.0.
  * Refactor: extract all library logic into src/lib.rs with full rustdoc.
  * Add 28 unit tests covering sanitize_filename, build_tasks, DownloadStatus,
    decompress_gzip, decompress_brotli, and save_journal (journal round-trip).
  * Add tempfile dev-dependency for hermetic journal tests.
  * Document every public type and function with /// and //! doc comments.
  * Add [lib] and [[bin]] targets to Cargo.toml for clean lib/binary split.
  * src/main.rs is now a thin, documented CLI wrapper delegating to the lib.
  * Improve final summary output with ✓ / ✗ per-file indicators.

 -- Alexander Salas Bastidas <ajsb85@firechip.dev>  Thu, 29 May 2026 08:12:00 +0200

